>[Thoughts]
>

If you don't move the pieces, I think the best you can do is to
cut the doughnut into 9 pieces.  If you can move the pieces,
you can get up to 18 by arranging it so that the cuts, after
the first, go through the part that was next to the hole to
make three pieces out of each original piece.


